Benefits
Make customer service your competitive edge
Offer nonstop service
Rest easy knowing AI agents provide instant support to your customers anytime, anywhere—shrinking ticket queues.
Quick time to value
AI agents are flexible and work in any customer situation. They're easy to set up and don't require a babysitter.
Delight customers
Boost CSAT with personalization. AI agents are intuitive and deepen their understanding to make every interaction better.
Act on real insights
Know how to get the best out of every AI agent. Closely monitor how your agents are performing with our robust analytics suite.
Features
Scale on the road to +80% automation
Connect your AI agent to your knowledge base and use Generative AI to answer FAQs. Increase first contact resolution and achieve 10% automation.
Resolve more sophisticated questions with conversation flows that are easy to build, guiding customers to their desired answers. Add control and customization to your AI agent, achieving 20% automation rates.
Solve interactions from start to finish with connected backend systems using APIs that control how your AI agent responds. Authenticate customers, provide personalized responses, and reach 40% automation rates.
Perfect conversation flows with actionable analytics that give you visibility into areas of improvement. Use QA to detect issues, maximize your processes, and achieve 60% automation.
Drive success with customer insights and expand to new use cases, channels, languages, and markets and reach beyond +80% automation.
