Frequently asked questions
Zendesk AI agents are available to all Zendesk customers on Support and Suite plans.
AI agents use Generative AI and Zendesk proprietary intent models. You get the most accurate, high-functioning, human-like experience when put together.
AI agents work across all social, web, mobile, and email channels.
AI agents support 109 languages at native fluency that automatically switches based on customer input, providing your customers a personalized experience.
AI agents are priced by automated resolution (AR). Each Zendesk plan comes with a number of free ARs, so it’s easy to get started.
